01:40.233 --> 01:41.234
How well you're looking.

01:41.234 --> 01:42.535
Oh, thank you.

01:42.535 --> 01:43.229
I like your suit.

01:43.536 --> 01:44.537
Well, you're too kind.

01:44.537 --> 01:46.539
And it's nice to see you again.

01:46.539 --> 01:48.241
Bye-bye.

01:48.241 --> 01:50.243
Take care.

01:50.243 --> 01:51.437
Wow, that was thorough.

01:51.811 --> 01:53.870
Find any polyps up there?

01:56.816 --> 01:59.385
