02:02.322 --> 02:03.690
Hey! Barry, hi.

02:03.690 --> 02:06.181
This is Frasier and Niles...

02:06.693 --> 02:07.694
and Martin.

02:07.694 --> 02:08.695
Hi. Hi.

02:08.695 --> 02:10.697
Whoa, strong handshake.

02:10.697 --> 02:12.365
You look like you work out a lot.

02:12.365 --> 02:14.458
