02:50.370 --> 02:52.304
The muscles.

02:54.240 --> 02:55.575
Good point, Dad.

02:55.575 --> 02:57.566
second tip-off; no poodle.

02:59.445 --> 03:02.282
so, isn't he fabulous?

03:02.282 --> 03:05.885
Yes, yes, uh, fabulous
sums it up in a word.

03:05.885 --> 03:08.388
I think he's perfect
for you, Roz--

03:08.388 --> 03:11.255
