03:20.300 --> 03:21.597
Because he takes care of himself?

03:22.302 --> 03:24.304
That is just such lazy, stereotypical...

03:24.304 --> 03:26.306
You're right; it was a
shallow knee-jerk assumption

03:26.306 --> 03:27.607
and unworthy of us both

03:27.607 --> 03:28.869
as psychiatrists and men about town.

03:31.411 --> 03:33.379
We better go. We're
going to miss the movie.

03:33.680 --> 03:34.681
Right. Bye.

03:34.681 --> 03:35.670
No biscotti for you?

03:36.382 --> 03:37.371
Please. I'm a house.

