03:50.997 --> 03:52.498
in these ridiculous shorts of yours.

03:52.498 --> 03:54.000
You wouldn't need them

03:54.000 --> 03:55.501
if you hadn't burs t out of your own.

03:55.501 --> 03:56.490
I did not burst out of them.

03:57.003 --> 03:58.504
My laundress simply over bleached them

03:58.504 --> 04:01.007
