What sort of place do you think that is?

04:33.806 --> 04:35.308
Well, let's see.

04:35.308 --> 04:37.810
Tuesday is leather night,

04:37.810 --> 04:40.643
so it's probably some
sort of shoe outlet.

04:43.283 --> 04:44.284
