04:48.588 --> 04:50.283
I was seeing patients until 7:00.

04:50.590 --> 04:52.292
If I'm late, she might get suspicious.

04:52.292 --> 04:53.993
Niles, Roz is my friend.

04:53.993 --> 04:54.994
