04:54.994 --> 04:56.996
by some man who's lying
to her about himself.

04:56.996 --> 04:58.486
I'll be just a minute.

05:05.004 --> 05:07.507
Excuse me. Uh, I'm looking for a guy.

05:07.507 --> 05:09.873
Yeah, I kind of got
that from the shorts.

05:11.344 --> 05:12.333
It's a particular guy.

05:12.845 --> 05:13.846
He's about 35 years...

05:13.846 --> 05:14.847
Frasier?

05:14.847 --> 05:16.349
Eduardo!

05:16.349 --> 05:20.353
My furniture polisher.

05:20.353 --> 05:22.355
Don't tell me you put
away paste and chamois

05:22.355 --> 05:23.356
for life as a barkeep.

05:23.356 --> 05:24.957
