surprised to see me in here.

05:27.527 --> 05:29.154
Okay.

05:30.830 --> 05:31.922
All right, look,

05:32.398 --> 05:33.900
I thought I saw a friend
of mine come in here.

05:33.900 --> 05:37.631
He's, uh, mid-30s, uh,
wavy hair, good build.

05:37.904 --> 05:38.971
