this dark yet inevitable day.

09:12.585 --> 09:14.587
I so wish you could have
been allowed to come out

09:14.587 --> 09:16.589
in a time and manner
of your own choosing

09:16.589 --> 09:19.091
instead of being
wrenched from your closet,

09:19.091 --> 09:21.582
your voice cracking, your
cheeks crimson with shame.

09:22.094 --> 09:24.564
Gil, I am not gay.

09:24.564 --> 09:26.065
Oh, Frasier, you can't play coy

09:26.065 --> 09:29.068
once you've been caught
traipsing around Bad Billy's

09:29.068 --> 09:31.070
in shorts that left
little to the imagination.

09:31.070 --> 09:32.572
They were not my shorts.

09:32.572 --> 09:35.074
I simply borrowed them
because my own had split

09:35.074 --> 09:36.576
when I bent over...

09:36.576 --> 09:38.578
Oh, please!

09:38.578 --> 09:41.080
