09:41.080 --> 09:43.082
I just want to say that your kACL family

09:43.082 --> 09:44.584
will be here for you

09:44.584 --> 09:46.074
as you take your first brave steps

09:46.586 --> 09:47.587
on that yellow brick road

09:47.587 --> 09:49.589
to pride and self
- acceptance and...

09:49.589 --> 09:52.080
