10:40.272 --> 10:42.775
"I am not even curious about... "

10:42.775 --> 10:45.266
Yes, all right!

10:45.778 --> 10:47.268
Thank you.

10:51.784 --> 10:53.786
Frasier.

10:53.786 --> 10:54.787
I see you caught my show.

10:54.787 --> 10:56.288
Mm-hmm.

10:56.288 --> 10:57.289
Go ahead. Let's hear it.

10:57.289 --> 10:59.792
I'm not going to tease
you. I'm grateful.

10:59.792 --> 11:01.260
You could have ratted me out to Daphne,

11:01.260 --> 11:03.262
but instead, you protected me...

11:03.262 --> 11:05.753
just like a big sister should.

11:07.767 --> 11:10.759
You know, I'm glad this tickles you.

11:11.270 --> 11:12.772
I shouldn't make fun.

11:12.772 --> 11:15.274
