12:16.001 --> 12:17.737
FRAsIER; I would love that.

12:17.737 --> 12:19.739
Let me just grab my coffee.

12:19.739 --> 12:20.728
Good-bye, Dad.

12:21.040 --> 12:21.734
Niles.

12:27.747 --> 12:29.749
Did you see that?

12:29.749 --> 12:32.051
